text: Flor de Caña (which means 'Sugarcane flower' in Spanish) is a type of premium rum that is made by the company, Compañía Licorera de Nicaragua. == History == The company started making this rum in the year 1890. == References == == Other websites == *Flor De Cana's Website Category:1890s establishments in North America Category:1890 establishments Category:Drink companies Category:Nicaraguan culture Category:Alcoholic spirits Category:Organizations based in Nicaragua
